Question 2️⃣ (Next Level)

Create a REST API using Spring Boot that returns a student name using PathVariable.

Requirement

Endpoint:

GET /student/{name}

Example request:

/student/Ravi

Expected response:

Hello Ravi
-----
@RestController
public class StudentController{
    @GetMapping("/student/{name}")
    public String studentNameDisplay(@PathVariable String name)
    {
        return "Hello "+name;
    }
}
